&lt;p&gt;Data and how it is used play a central role at Jampp and are at the heart of our product, business, operational, and financial decisions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Lead Machine Learning Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll be in charge of one of the most important and critical parts of our Architecture. The machine learning platform is a module of our bidder, responsible for predicting in less than 20 milliseconds which banner and price we should bid for a given auction. These predictions are a key success factor of Jampp economics and our client mobile applications performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is more than a technical role; you’ll be a creative product and technical contributor. You’ll use your experience to inform our engineering process and decisions when building new features and ensuring the scalability and availability of the entire product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU´LL DO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the ML team, including performance reviews, career development, and setting individual goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the long-term strategic roadmap for evolving ML solutions in alignment with business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and coordinate the execution of key initiatives, ensuring efficient delivery and providing visibility to stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, code and deploy highly scalable features (mostly in Python) from a massive machine-learning system that powers our economic module.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate different statistical models, taking into consideration the trade-off between model improvements vs scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join a team of data scientists, data engineers and software engineers to design, prototype and build scalable distributed systems that will be used to enhance the machine learning platform we have.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a self-sufficient, autonomous manner, striving through ambiguity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
