&lt;li&gt;Excellent engineering and strong CS fundamentals. (Hands-on programmer, not a data analyst).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience working with ML technologies and building model training pipelines.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
